Uhunoma Naomi Osazuwa (amụrụ Novemba 23, 1987 na Oakland, California) bụ nwaanyị onye u ọsọ egwuregw na-azọ mpi na egwuregwu nke a na-akpọ heptathlon
Ọ nochitere anya Naijiria na asọmi Olympik nke 2012 mana emechaghị na-asọmpi ahụ
O tozuru asọmpi Olympik nke 2016 na egwuregwu Hep, nke emechara na okwa onye iri abụọ na itoolu.
Ọ nwetara nzere PhD maka mmuta ọgwu na 2014 site na Mahadum Michigan College of Pharmacy.
